OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start this
OL,6,Fmorning, but the cloud will gradually
OL,7,Flift and burn away to give a sunny
OL,8,Fafternoon for most. Feeling very warm
OL,9,Fin the strong sunshine and lighter
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine and sunny evening will
OL,13,Flead to a largely clear night. Patchy
OL,14,Fmist and cloud however will reform
OL,15,Flater. A warm night, especially in
OL,16,Furban areas.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,19,Fonce any early morning low cloud and
OL,20,Fmist clears. Feeling very warm,
OL,21,Fespecially in the strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
